This is related to [this bug report](https://github.com/python/mypy/issues/15148) in the mypy type tracker.

```python
class A: ...

@final
class D: ...

def func4(val: D):
    if isinstance(val, A):
        reveal_type(val, expected_text="Never") # Currently produces <subtype of A and D>
```
